I'm Xu Miyu,

580
00:25:31,270 --> 00:25:32,750
an attendant from the HSKP Department
at Purong Hotel.

581
00:25:32,750 --> 00:25:34,200
Xu Miyu?

582
00:25:35,720 --> 00:25:36,920
This stubborn old man

583
00:25:37,160 --> 00:25:38,490
must have troubled you.

584
00:25:39,000 --> 00:25:40,260
Not at all. It's my job.

585
00:25:41,480 --> 00:25:42,880
Is Tan Jiaming's family here?

586
00:25:42,880 --> 00:25:44,510
Please go through the
admission procedures.

587
00:25:44,510 --> 00:25:45,160
I'll go.

588
00:25:45,880 --> 00:25:46,400
Here.

589
00:25:47,270 --> 00:25:48,480
Take this bank card.

590
00:25:49,680 --> 00:25:51,400
The PIN is 330915.

591
00:25:51,400 --> 00:25:52,330
Okay, thank you.

592
00:25:57,270 --> 00:25:58,720
You even know how to hide it, huh?

593
00:25:58,720 --> 00:25:59,960
If Jizhou hadn't

594
00:26:00,200 --> 00:26:01,880
called me early this morning,

595
00:26:02,160 --> 00:26:03,440
I wouldn't have come to the hospital

596
00:26:03,440 --> 00:26:05,000
and wasted my time with you.

597
00:26:05,680 --> 00:26:07,300
You had a heart attack!

598
00:26:07,640 --> 00:26:09,570
Don't you know how serious that is?

599
00:26:10,160 --> 00:26:11,030
It's an old problem.

600
00:26:11,030 --> 00:26:12,400
Doctors just like to scare people.

601
00:26:12,400 --> 00:26:14,060
They make it sound so serious.

602
00:26:14,550 --> 00:26:15,480
Ms. An,

603
00:26:15,790 --> 00:26:17,280
the guest in 1810

604
00:26:17,310 --> 00:26:19,040
needs to be hospitalized
for observation for a few days.

605
00:26:19,040 --> 00:26:20,320
His family has arrived.

606
00:26:19,260 --> 00:26:22,960
[Nurse Station]

607
00:26:20,380 --> 00:26:22,000
Okay, come back first.

608
00:26:22,450 --> 00:26:23,980
I've already told Ms. Zhang

609
00:26:24,000 --> 00:26:26,000
about your performance last night.

610
00:26:26,030 --> 00:26:26,790
Thank you, Ms. An.

611
00:26:26,790 --> 00:26:28,000
It's all part of my job.

612
00:26:28,000 --> 00:26:28,720
Thank you.

613
00:26:29,160 --> 00:26:29,720
Okay.

614
00:26:31,690 --> 00:26:33,080
I'm sorry, Ms. An.

615
00:26:33,310 --> 00:26:34,790
I was on shift rotation yesterday

616
00:26:34,790 --> 00:26:35,920
and was with my kid for an exam.

617
00:26:35,920 --> 00:26:37,030
My phone was off.

618
00:26:37,240 --> 00:26:38,500
Sorry for the trouble.

619
00:26:38,680 --> 00:26:39,680
It was no trouble.

620
00:26:39,920 --> 00:26:41,030
I'm actually happy for you.

621
00:26:41,030 --> 00:26:42,400
The attendant under you

622
00:26:42,400 --> 00:26:43,950
is so responsible

623
00:26:44,160 --> 00:26:45,400
and quick to react.

624
00:26:45,720 --> 00:26:46,720
She handled

625
00:26:46,720 --> 00:26:47,960
such an urgent situation

626
00:26:47,960 --> 00:26:49,160
perfectly in no time.

627
00:26:49,400 --> 00:26:51,070
The guest is out of danger now,

628
00:26:51,350 --> 00:26:52,680
so we are all relieved.

629
00:26:53,550 --> 00:26:54,240
The guest's family

630
00:26:54,240 --> 00:26:55,750
even called from abroad

631
00:26:55,750 --> 00:26:56,960
to thank our hotel.

632
00:26:57,590 --> 00:26:59,030
The attendants on your executive floor

633
00:26:59,030 --> 00:27:00,240
deserve the most praise.

634
00:27:00,240 --> 00:27:00,990
No problem.

635
00:27:01,200 --> 00:27:03,000
I'll definitely praise her
when I get back.

636
00:27:03,000 --> 00:27:04,060
Excuse me, cousin.

637
00:27:04,400 --> 00:27:05,750
Go help me get something.

638
00:27:05,750 --> 00:27:07,210
It's in the jacket pocket.

639
00:27:11,790 --> 00:27:12,390
Is it this?

640
00:27:16,200 --> 00:27:17,030
Look.

641
00:27:18,030 --> 00:27:18,720
Ahui

642
00:27:19,720 --> 00:27:20,810
is already gone.

643
00:27:21,750 --> 00:27:23,810
I went to his house yesterday morning

644
00:27:23,880 --> 00:27:25,080
and happened to catch

645
00:27:26,000 --> 00:27:27,920
the seventh day of his passing.

646
00:27:28,680 --> 00:27:30,550
The one in the middle is Liang.

647
00:27:31,070 --> 00:27:32,720
When I went to see him,

648
00:27:33,070 --> 00:27:35,400
he just stared at me blankly,

649
00:27:35,960 --> 00:27:37,240
shedding tears,

650
00:27:37,550 --> 00:27:39,110
unable to say a word.

651
00:27:40,510 --> 00:27:42,310
He has been paralyzed for a year.

652
00:27:43,240 --> 00:27:44,030
In the end,

653
00:27:44,480 --> 00:27:45,160
Ming

654
00:27:45,720 --> 00:27:48,650
was taken to Shenzhen
by his daughter to settle down.

655
00:27:49,200 --> 00:27:51,240
I am the only one left.

656
00:27:55,270 --> 00:27:56,680
Decades have passed.

657
00:27:59,680 --> 00:28:00,720
It went too fast.

658
00:28:02,230 --> 00:28:06,240
[Gao Hong-19th Floor-Rest shift]
[Luo Qingping-18th Floor-Day shift ]

659
00:28:06,260 --> 00:28:11,790
[Yin Xiang-18th Floor-Day shift
-Positive feedback]

660
00:28:12,030 --> 00:28:12,790
Last night,

661
00:28:13,030 --> 00:28:15,760
the guest in 1810
suffered a sudden heart attack.

662
00:28:15,790 --> 00:28:17,250
Yin Xiang, who was on duty,

663
00:28:17,270 --> 00:28:19,240
immediately reported to
the relevant hotel departments

664
00:28:19,240 --> 00:28:21,240
and rushed the patient
to the hospital in time.

665
00:28:21,240 --> 00:28:22,640
She is hereby commended.

666
00:28:23,270 --> 00:28:24,310
Not bad, little Xiang.

667
00:28:24,310 --> 00:28:25,960
Why didn't you mention such a big thing?

668
00:28:25,960 --> 00:28:28,160
Treat us to a meal when you get the bonus.

669
00:28:29,750 --> 00:28:30,310
Miyu,

670
00:28:30,960 --> 00:28:32,090
don't be late again.

671
00:28:32,920 --> 00:28:33,510
Got it.

672
00:28:35,200 --> 00:28:36,890
Everyone, cheer up.

673
00:28:37,000 --> 00:28:39,440
This month is
the service quality supervision month.

674
00:28:39,440 --> 00:28:41,570
Don't slack off or be late.

675
00:28:41,750 --> 00:28:44,030
If you ruin the reputation
of the HSKP Department,

676
00:28:44,030 --> 00:28:45,750
I can't protect you in front of Mr. Feng.

677
00:28:45,750 --> 00:28:46,480
Understood?

678
00:28:46,480 --> 00:28:47,620
Understood.

679
00:28:47,750 --> 00:28:48,550
Get to work.

680
00:29:10,550 --> 00:29:11,400
Miyu.

681
00:29:17,400 --> 00:29:18,110
Yin Xiang.

682
00:29:20,000 --> 00:29:22,000
Don't you have anything to say to me?

683
00:29:22,030 --> 00:29:22,550
I...

684
00:29:24,400 --> 00:29:25,170
Miyu.

685
00:29:26,030 --> 00:29:28,070
I didn't mean to steal your credit.

686
00:29:28,790 --> 00:29:31,240
A life-threatening incident
happened last night.

687
00:29:31,240 --> 00:29:33,500
I was afraid that if the management knew,

688
00:29:34,000 --> 00:29:35,860
I would lose my salary this month.

689
00:29:38,240 --> 00:29:39,360
Don't be mad.

690
00:29:40,550 --> 00:29:42,210
Please don't expose me, okay?

691
00:29:44,290 --> 00:29:45,300
You have it hard.

692
00:29:46,030 --> 00:29:47,090
We all have it hard.

693
00:29:48,510 --> 00:29:50,510
We both work on the executive floor.

694
00:29:50,550 --> 00:29:52,880
We inevitably need to help each other out,

695
00:29:53,440 --> 00:29:54,480
right?

696
00:29:55,440 --> 00:29:56,570
I understand, Miyu.

697
00:29:56,720 --> 00:29:57,780
I owe you this time.

698
00:29:58,000 --> 00:29:59,000
Next time you need me,

699
00:29:59,000 --> 00:30:00,530
I will definitely help you.

700
00:30:22,750 --> 00:30:23,480
Take a break.

701
00:30:24,980 --> 00:30:25,580
Thank you.

702
00:30:32,880 --> 00:30:34,610
You are an interesting person.

703
00:30:35,440 --> 00:30:36,970
When a bad review
that shouldn't fall on you

704
00:30:36,970 --> 00:30:38,830
was pinned on you, you endured it.

705
00:30:39,590 --> 00:30:41,160
When the good review
that rightfully belonged to you

706
00:30:41,160 --> 00:30:42,160
went to someone else,

707
00:30:42,160 --> 00:30:43,360
you still endured it.

708
00:30:43,510 --> 00:30:44,510
Are you

709
00:30:45,030 --> 00:30:46,200
a people pleaser?

710
00:30:54,200 --> 00:30:55,240
I am not trying to please anyone.

711
00:30:55,240 --> 00:30:58,640
I just think everyone
has their own difficulties,

712
00:30:58,750 --> 00:31:01,350
and I don't want to
make things hard for others.

713
00:31:15,270 --> 00:31:16,000
What is it now?

714
00:31:16,000 --> 00:31:17,240
I want to ask you a favor.

715
00:31:17,240 --> 00:31:18,280
Ask me?

716
00:31:18,510 --> 00:31:20,270
Could you go to any room

717
00:31:20,790 --> 00:31:22,030
on the executive floor

718
00:31:22,030 --> 00:31:24,150
and get me a bottle of shampoo,

719
00:31:24,960 --> 00:31:26,720
then go to the storage room

720
00:31:26,720 --> 00:31:28,030
and take a new one—

721
00:31:28,750 --> 00:31:30,440
one that has just been
logged into inventory?

722
00:31:30,440 --> 00:31:30,880
Why...

723
00:31:30,880 --> 00:31:31,810
Don't ask me why.

724
00:31:32,430 --> 00:31:34,030
Just tell me if you can or not.

725
00:31:36,290 --> 00:31:37,030
Sure.

726
00:31:38,720 --> 00:31:40,180
But you can't tell anyone.

727
00:31:40,480 --> 00:31:41,880
Because I only trust you.

728
00:32:10,640 --> 00:32:13,070
[Shower Gel]

729
00:32:17,910 --> 00:32:19,210
[Shampoo]

730
00:32:27,510 --> 00:32:28,270
Miyu.

731
00:32:28,440 --> 00:32:29,070
Ms. Zhang.

732
00:32:38,080 --> 00:32:42,240
[1817 Empty]

733
00:32:57,750 --> 00:32:59,270
[Conditioner] [Shower Gel]

734
00:33:08,640 --> 00:33:09,650
Room service.

735
00:33:11,920 --> 00:33:12,850
Come in.

736
00:33:24,480 --> 00:33:25,280
Did you get it?

737
00:33:27,340 --> 00:33:31,080
[Shampoo] [Storage]

738
00:33:30,680 --> 00:33:31,280
Remember,

739
00:33:31,680 --> 00:33:32,960
keep today's matter a secret.

740
00:33:32,960 --> 00:33:35,020
You absolutely must not tell anyone.

741
00:33:36,400 --> 00:33:37,660
Then I have a question.

742
00:33:38,070 --> 00:33:39,450
Can you guarantee

743
00:33:39,790 --> 00:33:40,480
that this

744
00:33:40,480 --> 00:33:42,790
won't affect the hotel's
normal service operations?

745
00:33:42,790 --> 00:33:44,680
Are you bargaining with a guest?

746
00:33:45,960 --> 00:33:46,960
It's my duty.

747
00:33:49,440 --> 00:33:49,920
Okay.

748
00:33:50,240 --> 00:33:50,970
Don't worry.

749
00:34:08,320 --> 00:34:09,920
Can we pause tomorrow's shipment

750
00:34:09,920 --> 00:34:11,480
for a bit before sending it out?

751
00:34:11,480 --> 00:34:13,960
The prepaid payment has already
gone into your pocket.

752
00:34:13,960 --> 00:34:15,510
How can you cut off the supply?

753
00:34:15,510 --> 00:34:16,710
The goods aren't ready?

754
00:34:16,710 --> 00:34:18,150
It's not about the goods.

755
00:34:18,550 --> 00:34:19,760
I'm worried

756
00:34:19,760 --> 00:34:21,230
that doing this is too risky.

757
00:34:21,230 --> 00:34:22,690
What if someone finds out?

758
00:34:23,400 --> 00:34:25,320
Who could possibly find out?

759
00:34:25,760 --> 00:34:28,420
There's an attendant
on our floor named Xu Miyu.

760
00:34:28,510 --> 00:34:29,670
Xu Miyu?

761
00:34:30,630 --> 00:34:31,230
Who is she?

762
00:34:32,070 --> 00:34:32,880
A newbie.

763
00:34:34,719 --> 00:34:35,590
A rookie,

764
00:34:35,590 --> 00:34:36,510
and you can't handle her?

765
00:34:36,510 --> 00:34:37,320
No.

766
00:34:37,710 --> 00:34:38,630
I saw...

767
00:34:39,480 --> 00:34:40,760
I saw her take a bottle of shampoo

768
00:34:40,760 --> 00:34:43,260
from a guest room in a baffling way.

769
00:34:43,400 --> 00:34:44,760
I don't know what she's doing.

770
00:34:44,760 --> 00:34:46,090
And I didn't dare to ask.

771
00:34:46,190 --> 00:34:47,000
I'm worried

772
00:34:47,320 --> 00:34:49,280
she might have found out something.

773
00:34:49,280 --> 00:34:50,010
Zhang Cailu,

774
00:34:50,230 --> 00:34:51,090
let me tell you,

775
00:34:51,150 --> 00:34:52,860
get things straightened out.

776
00:34:53,070 --> 00:34:53,710
Are you the forewoman,

777
00:34:53,710 --> 00:34:54,400
or is she?

778
00:34:54,710 --> 00:34:56,400
You can't manage

779
00:34:56,400 --> 00:34:57,330
a new attendant?

780
00:34:57,510 --> 00:34:58,510
Do you still want to take your daughter

781
00:34:58,510 --> 00:34:59,960
to the Maldives for New Year's Eve?

782
00:34:59,960 --> 00:35:01,580
Yes, of course I do.

783
00:35:01,960 --> 00:35:05,000
But I'm on edge every day.

784
00:35:06,070 --> 00:35:07,630
The pressure is overwhelming.

785
00:35:07,630 --> 00:35:09,000
My body can't take it.

786
00:35:10,510 --> 00:35:12,000
Why didn't you say that

787
00:35:12,000 --> 00:35:13,330
when you took the money?

788
00:35:13,480 --> 00:35:14,550
You just want to make money

789
00:35:14,550 --> 00:35:15,880
without taking responsibility.

790
00:35:15,880 --> 00:35:17,710
If your body really can't take it,
stop doing it.

791
00:35:17,710 --> 00:35:19,840
There are plenty of people who want to.

792
00:35:20,110 --> 00:35:21,150
No, no.

793
00:35:22,030 --> 00:35:23,360
I don't mean any of that.

794
00:35:23,400 --> 00:35:24,220
I mean,

795
00:35:24,510 --> 00:35:25,230
I definitely won't let

796
00:35:25,230 --> 00:35:26,560
that Xu Miyu off.

797
00:35:26,800 --> 00:35:28,070
In a few days, I'll find a random excuse

798
00:35:28,070 --> 00:35:29,110
to fire her.

799
00:35:29,590 --> 00:35:31,510
I definitely won't cause you any trouble.

800
00:35:31,510 --> 00:35:33,070
I don't care how you do it.

801
00:35:33,070 --> 00:35:34,590
Make it look good.

802
00:35:34,800 --> 00:35:35,800
Don't delay my plans!

803
00:35:35,800 --> 00:35:36,400
Okay.

804
00:35:36,550 --> 00:35:37,350
Rest assured.

805
00:36:01,070 --> 00:36:01,760
Miyu.

806
00:36:04,960 --> 00:36:05,860
Um...

807
00:36:07,510 --> 00:36:08,630
Are you

808
00:36:09,230 --> 00:36:10,290
a people-pleaser?

809
00:36:10,920 --> 00:36:12,510
Don't tell me you want to change shifts.

810
00:36:12,510 --> 00:36:13,110
I don't have time.

811
00:36:13,110 --> 00:36:14,640
I'm not changing shifts.

812
00:36:15,150 --> 00:36:15,760
I...

813
00:36:18,840 --> 00:36:20,440
I want to tell you something.

814
00:36:20,960 --> 00:36:22,070
Here you are.

815
00:36:25,360 --> 00:36:26,760
What are you talking about?

816
00:36:26,760 --> 00:36:27,760
N... Nothing.

817
00:36:28,840 --> 00:36:30,000
I was going to ask you something.

818
00:36:30,000 --> 00:36:32,460
Was your leave for tomorrow
approved or not?

819
00:36:54,710 --> 00:36:56,350
I don't need help.

820
00:36:56,470 --> 00:36:57,550
Welcome to Purong Hotel.

821
00:36:57,550 --> 00:36:58,190
After you, Princess.

822
00:36:58,190 --> 00:36:58,710
Please.

823
00:37:11,630 --> 00:37:12,480
Welcome back.

824
00:37:12,480 --> 00:37:13,190
Mr. Tan.

825
00:37:13,510 --> 00:37:14,670
We meet again,

826
00:37:14,760 --> 00:37:15,550
Xu Miyu.

827
00:37:19,360 --> 00:37:20,590
What is this?

828
00:37:21,400 --> 00:37:23,800
This is a safety handrail
prepared for you.

829
00:37:24,030 --> 00:37:25,360
Why wouldn't I be safe?

830
00:37:25,360 --> 00:37:26,590
Am I that old?

831
00:37:27,150 --> 00:37:28,620
How old are you?

832
00:37:28,920 --> 00:37:30,360
Don't be ungrateful.

833
00:37:45,710 --> 00:37:47,770
That's very thoughtful of you, Miyu.

834
00:37:48,630 --> 00:37:50,000
Very thoughtful, Miyu.

835
00:37:50,150 --> 00:37:51,760
I can use it

836
00:37:51,760 --> 00:37:53,220
for exercise and fitness.

837
00:37:53,650 --> 00:37:54,800
Be careful.

838
00:37:55,230 --> 00:37:56,040
Watch out.

839
00:37:59,550 --> 00:38:00,510
Mr. Tan.

840
00:38:02,550 --> 00:38:04,360
You old rascal.

841
00:38:04,710 --> 00:38:06,030
I am old.

842
00:38:07,230 --> 00:38:07,840
Miyu,

843
00:38:07,840 --> 00:38:08,760
you're really thoughtful.

844
00:38:08,760 --> 00:38:09,590
Thank you.

845
00:38:09,590 --> 00:38:10,360
Come here.

846
00:38:10,480 --> 00:38:11,740
Take a break. Sit down.

847
00:38:30,280 --> 00:38:31,480
[5:00 AM, Monday, Back Kitchen Door]

848
00:38:37,540 --> 00:38:47,330
[Back Kitchen Area—No Unauthorized Entry]

849
00:38:50,090 --> 00:38:50,650
[Back Kitchen Area—No Unauthorized Entry]

850
00:38:52,210 --> 00:38:53,950
[Back Kitchen Area—No Unauthorized Entry]

851
00:38:57,560 --> 00:38:57,820
[Loading]

852
00:38:57,980 --> 00:38:59,450
[Deposit to someone]

853
00:39:28,630 --> 00:39:29,630
You startled me.

854
00:39:47,630 --> 00:39:49,230
Does it still taste the same?

855
00:39:51,510 --> 00:39:52,960
Have you really not eaten

856
00:39:52,960 --> 00:39:53,600
in ages?

857
00:39:55,440 --> 00:39:56,440
That's going too far.

858
00:39:56,440 --> 00:39:58,970
Are you even snatching food
from your senior?

859
00:39:59,070 --> 00:39:59,870
Here, senior.

860
00:40:01,070 --> 00:40:01,670
Boss,

861
00:40:02,150 --> 00:40:03,960
another steamer of soup dumplings, please.

862
00:40:03,960 --> 00:40:04,480
Coming.

863
00:40:06,110 --> 00:40:07,570
You really do love eating,

864
00:40:07,960 --> 00:40:10,070
or are you just pretending to
be nostalgic about home?

865
00:40:10,070 --> 00:40:11,800
Senior, you are like a food map.

866
00:40:11,880 --> 00:40:14,070
It's a pity you're in the
Finance Department.

867
00:40:14,070 --> 00:40:15,550
You should go to the Marketing Department

868
00:40:15,550 --> 00:40:16,480
or the sales department.

869
00:40:16,480 --> 00:40:18,140
The F&B Department works too.

870
00:40:19,030 --> 00:40:21,110
I'll take that as a compliment
on my versatility.

871
00:40:21,110 --> 00:40:22,510
As for the skills of eating,

872
00:40:22,510 --> 00:40:24,170
I will teach you slowly later.

873
00:40:24,550 --> 00:40:25,480
Whatever I ask you next,

874
00:40:25,480 --> 00:40:26,360
just answer it.

875
00:40:26,960 --> 00:40:28,620
Promise me you won't pretend.

876
00:40:28,960 --> 00:40:29,890
First question.

877
00:40:30,070 --> 00:40:32,670
Why did you go to
the kitchen's back door today?

878
00:40:34,150 --> 00:40:35,710
Didn't you encourage me to?

879
00:40:41,550 --> 00:40:42,120
Yes.

880
00:40:43,510 --> 00:40:44,150
I want to know

881
00:40:44,150 --> 00:40:45,360
what today's Purong Hotel

882
00:40:45,360 --> 00:40:46,680
has really become.

883
00:40:46,760 --> 00:40:48,820
So, what do you think after seeing it?

884
00:40:49,510 --> 00:40:50,840
The great tree of Purong

885
00:40:51,550 --> 00:40:52,590
looks glorious on the outside,

886
00:40:52,590 --> 00:40:53,450
but in reality,

887
00:40:53,710 --> 00:40:55,070
it has been hollowed out
by termites on the inside.

888
00:40:55,070 --> 00:40:55,550
Okay.

889
00:40:55,590 --> 00:40:56,590
Second question.

890
00:40:57,190 --> 00:40:58,450
Coming back this time,

891
00:40:58,670 --> 00:40:59,880
what exactly are you here for?

